So in my grade, we have this girl called...um, 'Jasmine' (not her real name) and she was a spoiled brat. she had a 'mansion' (she really just had an apartment) and '1 million dollars' (keep in mind we were very young at the time) and everyone hated her. she made people cry, bullied people and played harmful pranks. guess what? she had an a p p l e w a t c h. so, we got to pull a prank oh HER.

We stole her apple watch.

and our friend hid it at her house since she was the only person with a single parent and no siblings. but out SOME outcome, her dad caught her. so she had to give the apple watch back in front of her dad...so my OTHER friend pretended to be Jasmine. unfortunately, didn't work.

back at school, Jasmine was having a heart attack but my friend gave it back (sad). Jasmine thanked her and gave her a box of candy as a gift.

free candy
she got free candy

THE END
